Package com.pacman.model.managers

Class CollectableManager

java.lang.Object
com.pacman.model.managers.CollectableManager
public class CollectableManager
extends java.lang.Object
Class used to manage collectable items. Collectable items are {DOT, GUN, CHERRIES, BERRIES, CUP} Creates item. Stores items in a list. Calls it draw() method Calls it checkCollision() method to detect collision with player and take proper action.

      public Collectable.Type checkCollision​(java.awt.Rectangle hitBox, Map map)
      Checks collision with collectable items one by one If any of collectable items intersects with given hitBox method returns the type of this collectable item. If none of collectable items intersects with give hitBox method returns the null Collectable.Type or Null
